'''Pat Robertson''' (Not to be confused with [[Twilight|Rob Patterson]]) is a [[politics|politically]] motivated, [[batshit insane]] [[cult|evangelical]] preacher who who runs the [[BDSM|Cock and Ball Network]] (CBN) to cater to the secret [[gay]] needs of [[Christians]] everywhere.  His main form of [[Auto_erotic_asphyxiation|eroticism]] involves [[The_Rapture|doomsday]] preaching and how everyone is [[raped|fucked]] unless they accept [[Jesus]] into their hearts and [[party_hard|pray really hard.]]

Pat has been known to [[troll]] the media by making rather [[lulz]]y comments such as saying [[God]] gave Israeli leader Jew a stroke for giving Israeli-controlled land to [[Muslim|Palestinians]] and that [[unwarrented_self_importance|he caused]] hurricane Gloria to change course and [[fail|not hit]] the CBN headquarters through his [[fellatio|prayer.]]

==AIDS and Hitler==
Pat Robertson, [[god hates fags|much like God]], hates [[gay|fags]]. In fact, he hates them so much that he believes that [[AIDS]] is conspiring with gay people to help support the [[Illuminati|gay agenda]] by killing them. [[SRSLY]] you can't make this shit up.

He said: ''"Many Observers say that AIDS is the hammer and gun of the homosexual movement, an effective vehicle to propel the homosexual agenda throughout every phase of our society."''

This agenda of [[GRIDS]], [[fag|fags]], and automobiles is propelled by the Jewish Media Conspiracy, who are known to be sympathetic to gays, niggers, and [[GNAA | gay-niggers]]. This is ironic, as Robertson also believes that [[Hitler]] and his [[Hal Turner|followers]] were gay [[Satan|satanists]] stating: 

''"Many of those people involved with Adolf Hitler were Satanists, many of them were homosexuals -- the two things seem to go together."''
